name: rainy dream
description:
It was raining when I saw you.
You were standing beside me.
You looked at me, I looked at you too.
You smiled at me and I smiled at you too.
My heart beat faster than ever.
I wanted to ask your name, but suddenly rain stopped.
And you vanished from my dream.
Hope to get back the same dream.
So that I can at least ask ur name.
So that I can tell everyone the name of my first love.

Chonto Monto
